	</dd>
	<dd><a name="comment_266" ></a>
	<p><em><strong>Sam</strong> replies:</em> "All that is necessary for the triumph of evil is for good men to do nothing."</p> <p>If Labour are re-elected and you did nothing to stop them, then you may be good, but you did nothing, and evil triumphed.</p>
	<small>
