	<dd><a name="comment_301" ></a>
	<p><em><strong>TL</strong> replies:</em> "Do you think you won't have to accept those evils if you don't vote?"</p> <p>Most probably, yes. But I won't have facilitated them.</p> <p>How does voting for these evils (and thereby giving them legitimacy by actively supporting them) help the situation?</p> <p>You assume that there's a party in existence that has no policies that I find intolerable. If that were the case then I would have already voted a long time ago.</p> <p></p>
